firstObz.heading: Privacy Policy
firstObz.text: We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

secondObz.heading: 1. Purpose of Data Collection
secondObz.text: We collect your personal data, such as name and contact details, for the purpose of finding new orders and providing relevant services. The information helps us better understand the needs of users and improve our service.

thirdObz.heading: 2. Use of Data
thirdObz.text: The collected data is sent to our Telegram channel for further analysis and processing. This helps us respond to requests promptly and efficiently process new orders. We do not use your information for any purposes other than handling requests.

fourthObz.heading: 3. Security Measures
fourthObz.text: We take standard security measures to protect your data. All data we collect is transmitted through secure channels and is only stored for the duration of the session. We use modern technologies to prevent unauthorized access and data breaches. However, it is important to remember that transmitting data over the internet is never 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

fivthObz.heading: 4. Data Sharing with Third Parties
fivthObz.text: We do not share your data with third parties. All collected data is used exclusively for internal analysis and processing within our service. Your data remains confidential and is not used for marketing purposes or shared with external organizations.

sixthObz.heading: 5. Data Storage
sixthObz.text: We do not store your data on our servers. All collected data is immediately sent to Telegram for further processing and analysis and is not retained in any database. This means that your data is not stored on our server after being sent and is not used for any further purposes.

seventhObz.heading: Conclusion
seventhObz.text: By using our service, you agree to the terms of this privacy policy. If you have any questions or concerns about how your data is used, please feel free to contact us.
